text:
Never see such doctor in my whole life, see doctor for my neck and back pain.
Waiting for 3 hours to see doctor and doctor check me lesser than 30 seconds.
Just ask me wat problem,I replied.
Doctor said wait outside to collect your medicine.
He never check my bp, never check wat is the cause for pain whether muscle strain or anything else.
Wasted money and my good time.
I regret to choose acumed @Tuas.

It’s uncomfortable to see a doctor. Waiting for 3 hours won’t be your turn until someone else won’t go here to see a doctor again. It’s uncomfortable to wait until it’s dark and it’s your turn. What’s the concept of coming out within 10 seconds?
The doctor and admin staff are the worse. It seems like they just want to see as many patients as possible. Never coming back again.
